            <h3>29-Day Maximum Stay</h3>
            <p>In Vaughan, a short-term rental is defined as accommodation for 29 consecutive days or less. Rentals of 30+ days are considered long-term and exempt from STR regulations.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bylaw-card">
            <h3>License Required</h3>
            <p>All STR operators must obtain a license from the City. Both individual operators and STR brokerages require separate licenses. Your license number must appear on all listings and advertisements.</p>
          </div>
