            <h3>Principal Residence Only</h3>
            <p>Short-term rentals must be your principal residence, where you ordinarily reside and conduct daily affairs. Investment properties cannot be used for STRs in Vaughan.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bylaw-card">
            <h3>$2 Million Insurance</h3>
            <p>Operators must maintain liability insurance of at least $2,000,000 that specifically covers short-term rental activity. Proof of insurance is required for licensing.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bylaw-card">
            <h3>Vulnerable Sector Check</h3>
            <p>Vaughan requires a vulnerable sector check (more comprehensive than a standard criminal record check) as part of your license application.</p>
          </div>
